section.t:
 shows an example for the use of .sdnvseq for a part
of a structure using OIDs that could be used in ;
 shows the same with the .oid operator.

figure.sourcecode:
country-rdn = {country-oid => country-value}
country-oid = bytes .sdnvseq [85, 4, 6]
country-value = text .size 2

country-rdn = {country-oid => country-value}
country-oid = bytes .oid [2, 5, 4, 6]
country-value = text .size 2
